{"tid":1380442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宜/鍵戰] 發覺呢排文宜/鍵戰唔夠力水","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T06:42:36.000Z","uid":128522,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c7b22e204e72df0a3bb881452dd5d6dbaf43839","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:25:37.000Z","msg":"做乜呢排唔見晒文宜/鍵戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢場運動個頭開得咁好就係因為文宜做得好<br />\n你地無做錯到!<br />\n<br />\nA. 依家藍絲反擊點 &lt; 呢類希望可以直接靠人數反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1) 大陸仔係FB開假鬼佬AC 講英文<br />\n2) 長輩片 (CUT頭CUT尾 再配字)<br />\n3) 入黎連登係到周圍點火頭<br />\n<br />\nB. 新運動既資訊圖 &lt; 呢類係要方便大家SHARE / 貼圖, 保持唔同層面既資訊流通<br />\n1) 類似 21/7 元朗發生緊乜事既新聞圖<br />\n2) 新運動會日子<br />\n3) 其他要提醒手足既事項<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講「要分邊既人一早分晒邊」<br />\n仲有好多 淺藍 &lt;&gt; 淺黃搖擺緊既人, 係呢2日靠文宜既情況下, 又傾返向淺藍<br />\n<br />\n另外，請珍惜文宜兄弟姊妹, 唔好因為佢唔肯幫你整某一種你好想佢整既文宜<br />\n而對自己人開火 e.g. 有人唔鍾意整以牙還牙,  你唔好逼人啦好無<br />\n<br />\n我地要文宜, 文宜可以保障資訊正確流通, 吸納新血加入運動, 同埋Keep住士氣<br />\n勇武打完仗既時候，就到我地文宣組上場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859d3f8738653f492769fd86cb84258d0ea62cab","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"成日覺得整到文宜既巴絲打好有型<br />\n 利申, ART未合格過, 最高分拎D"},{"pid":"cab25b31408e7e601d90784098f87fc4befaa834","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跪求新文宣圖等我可以善用公司資源"},{"pid":"e0329222249d0b7b3f7894abd763b46947fd5622","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6431166d742fa48871a3c9a3ee0c92a415b4f5","tid":1380442,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18450bc08329f38b1421618f5188c2cad89150b","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:33:45.000Z","msg":"有無好有型有靘既文宣巴絲可以<br />\n教下小弟Art<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff20d8a743818fce175ecbe856a62914a02c614","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 文宣兄弟姊妹係味攰到訓晒啦"},{"pid":"bf57956d675dc9088d14f3026d5442645c850fe9","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d99a32493d2b9654dc15a956dd07134d645bbd4","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21161eef957dcb1faf5534ce0a47a369d21c2c79","tid":1380442,"uid":27198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:50:07.000Z","msg":"文宣唔係剩係整圖，文宣要有策略<br />\n<br />\n一個成功嘅marketing campaign要有幾個元素互相配合：<br />\n<br />\nAudience + Message + Creative + Media<br />\n<br />\n簡單嚟講，對一個群體嘅人（audience），用佢地接受嘅語言（message），喺接觸到佢地嘅場所（media），以佢地喜歡嘅形式（creative）講件事比佢聽<br />\n<br />\n例子：喺馬會門外向啲呀伯派長輩圖傳單連張「必贏六合彩飛」之類<br />\n<br />\n整圖只係creative嗰一part，冇方向咁做，事倍功半<br />\n<br />\n關係藍絲群眾嘅分析，可以睇徐緣篇文：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179701742127792?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F347912661973385%2Fposts%2F2179701742127792%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67RZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=eecc61cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179701742127792?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"8252ede21365b553a73384a71b176eb4360ac69b","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5d457b625f9fddcb793b04a17e6b9b68bc0e6f","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21161eef957dcb1faf5534ce0a47a369d21c2c79","tid":1380442,"uid":27198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:50:07.000Z","msg":"文宣唔係剩係整圖，文宣要有策略<br />\n<br />\n一個成功嘅marketing campaign要有幾個元素互相配合：<br />\n<br />\nAudience + Message + Creative + Media<br />\n<br />\n簡單嚟講，對一個群體嘅人（audience），用佢地接受嘅語言（message），喺接觸到佢地嘅場所（media），以佢地喜歡嘅形式（creative）講件事比佢聽<br />\n<br />\n例子：喺馬會門外向啲呀伯派長輩圖傳單連張「必贏六合彩飛」之類<br />\n<br />\n整圖只係creative嗰一part，冇方向咁做，事倍功半<br />\n<br />\n關係藍絲群眾嘅分析，可以睇徐緣篇文：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179701742127792?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F347912661973385%2Fposts%2F2179701742127792%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67RZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=eecc61cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179701742127792?sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"大哥有無橋可以比個方向文宣做野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9b7b9d403d6fdeee88b35a7cad23188cb2417e","tid":1380442,"uid":27198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f5d457b625f9fddcb793b04a17e6b9b68bc0e6f","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21161eef957dcb1faf5534ce0a47a369d21c2c79","tid":1380442,"uid":27198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:50:07.000Z","msg":"文宣唔係剩係整圖，文宣要有策略<br />\n<br />\n一個成功嘅marketing campaign要有幾個元素互相配合：<br />\n<br />\nAudience + Message + Creative + Media<br />\n<br />\n簡單嚟講，對一個群體嘅人（audience），用佢地接受嘅語言（message），喺接觸到佢地嘅場所（media），以佢地喜歡嘅形式（creative）講件事比佢聽<br />\n<br />\n例子：喺馬會門外向啲呀伯派長輩圖傳單連張「必贏六合彩飛」之類<br />\n<br />\n整圖只係creative嗰一part，冇方向咁做，事倍功半<br />\n<br />\n關係藍絲群眾嘅分析，可以睇徐緣篇文：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179701742127792?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F347912661973385%2Fposts%2F2179701742127792%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67RZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=eecc61cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179701742127792?sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"大哥有無橋可以比個方向文宣做野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:00:36.000Z","msg":"小弟都只係marketing 小薯仔，冇咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我諗最簡單可以針對淺黃、淺藍嘅人，針對性咁打一啲focus嘅message比佢地，坦白講而家太多資訊，正常人好難follow得晒，如果搵一兩單特別煲大，例如中聯辦葉虎事件，可能會更加有效"},{"pid":"d4be9e096e678bb7a96e025bece295faa5d5738f","tid":1380442,"uid":27198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"整圖嘅手足，可以諗一諗你想整比咩人睇，而你整出嚟嘅圖岩唔岩佢地睇<br />\n<br />\n長輩圖攻勢其實好有效，可以向呢個方向做多啲，比啲黑白分明易吸收嘅信息佢地，散播喺各區連儂牆"},{"pid":"ddf454fa5507fd832ed7d563569ea5d4e7690844","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a9b7b9d403d6fdeee88b35a7cad23188cb2417e","tid":1380442,"uid":27198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f5d457b625f9fddcb793b04a17e6b9b68bc0e6f","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21161eef957dcb1faf5534ce0a47a369d21c2c79","tid":1380442,"uid":27198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:50:07.000Z","msg":"文宣唔係剩係整圖，文宣要有策略<br />\n<br />\n一個成功嘅marketing campaign要有幾個元素互相配合：<br />\n<br />\nAudience + Message + Creative + Media<br />\n<br />\n簡單嚟講，對一個群體嘅人（audience），用佢地接受嘅語言（message），喺接觸到佢地嘅場所（media），以佢地喜歡嘅形式（creative）講件事比佢聽<br />\n<br />\n例子：喺馬會門外向啲呀伯派長輩圖傳單連張「必贏六合彩飛」之類<br />\n<br />\n整圖只係creative嗰一part，冇方向咁做，事倍功半<br />\n<br />\n關係藍絲群眾嘅分析，可以睇徐緣篇文：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179701742127792?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F347912661973385%2Fposts%2F2179701742127792%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67RZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=eecc61cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179701742127792?sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"大哥有無橋可以比個方向文宣做野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:00:36.000Z","msg":"小弟都只係marketing 小薯仔，冇咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我諗最簡單可以針對淺黃、淺藍嘅人，針對性咁打一啲focus嘅message比佢地，坦白講而家太多資訊，正常人好難follow得晒，如果搵一兩單特別煲大，例如中聯辦葉虎事件，可能會更加有效"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經好有方向, 多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81c6302d5c4f82ad4ab48a59d0ad2ac51ddbf50","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a5c008152608a474b846731675b2680dfda2f8","tid":1380442,"uid":265662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0393448ef37a70676205f0f9af17b77f5432f84","tid":1380442,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909a7c317c6376cf290a92ab2b8346a417e3abc6","tid":1380442,"uid":12